platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When it comes to getting the most out of your sleep, a tracker that can tell you much more than how many hours youve snoozed goes a long way. Rise does just that. It helps you understand how your activities impact your sleep health, and it focuses on sleep debt to help you close the gap between the sleep you need and the sleep you get.
This clever sleep tracker gives you a better understanding of how your activities impact your sleep health, and helps you close the gap between the sleep you need and the sleep you get.
